v 3
d surveye: SurvEye interactive Survey Solutions HTML dashboards from Stata
d
d SurvEye creates a polished interactive dashboard from a Survey Solutions
d questionnaire HTML file and the corresponding data in memory. Supports
d questionnaire and custom variables, smart variable families, subgroup comparisons,
d flexible sections, filters, highlights, discrete-count detection,
d native Stata weights, optional confidence intervals, outlier-aware numeric summaries,
d Arabic/Urdu right-to-left interfaces, Unicode, and optional Leaflet GPS maps
d with Google or OpenStreetMap base layers.
d
d Version: 2.1.2
d Requires: Stata 16 or newer
d Author: Attique Ur Rehman
d Affiliation: Enterprise Analysis Unit, World Bank
d Repository: https://github.com/arehman10/SurvEye
d Support: https://github.com/arehman10/SurvEye/issues
d Distribution-Date: 20260720
d License: MIT
d
f surveye.ado
f surveye.sthlp
F surveye.jar
F surveye_2_1_2.jar
f example.do
f README.md
f LICENSE
f THIRDPARTY-LICENSES.md
f CHANGELOG.md
e
